# Architecture Overview

## System Components

The platform is a FastAPI-based event ticketing system with async PostgreSQL, Redis rate limiting, Razorpay payments, and S3 media storage.

```
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│                    FastAPI Application                     │
│  lifespan → scheduler, Redis limiter init                 │
├──────────┬──────────┬──────────┬──────────┬────────────────┤
│  /api/user    /api/guest   /api/events   /api/organizers  │
│  /api/superadmin    /webhooks/razorpay    /api/core      │
└────┬────────────────┬─────────────────┬─────────────────┘
     │                 │                  │
     ▼                 ▼                  ▼
┌─────────┐     ┌──────────┐      ┌──────────────┐
│  Auth   │     │  Event   │      │  Payment     │
│ JWT +   │     │  Service │      │  Gateway     │
│ Cookies │     │  +       │      │  Razorpay    │
└────┬────┘     │  Scan    │      └──────┬───────┘
     │          │  Mgmt    │             │
     │          └────┬─────┘             │
     │               │                  │
     ▼               ▼                  ▼
┌─────────┐     ┌──────────────────────────────┐
│  User   │     │       Ticketing / Allocation  │
│  Guest  │     │  TicketType → DayAllocation  │
│  Super  │     │  Ticket → TicketHolder      │
│  Admin  │     │  Order → Allocation         │
└────┬────┘     └──────────────┬───────────────┘
     │                         │
     ▼                         ▼
┌─────────────────────────────────────┐
│          PostgreSQL (asyncpg)        │
│  async session factory + engine     │
└─────────────────────────────────────┘
     │
     ▼
┌─────────────┐     ┌──────────────┐     ┌──────────────┐
│   Redis    │     │   LocalStack │     │   NATS       │
│ Rate limit │     │   S3 (media) │     │   Workers    │
└─────────────┘     └──────────────┘     └──────────────┘
```

## Data Flow

### 1. Online Ticket Purchase

```
sequenceDiagram
    Customer->>API: POST /api/events/purchase/create
    API->>TicketingService: create_order()
    TicketingService->>TicketingRepository: lock_tickets()
    TicketingService->>Razorpay: create_order()
    TicketingService-->>Customer: order + gateway_order_id
    Note over Customer: Pays via Razorpay
    Razorpay->>Webhook: order.paid
    WebhookHandler->>OrderModel: update status=paid
    WebhookHandler->>AllocationModel: create (pool→buyer)
    WebhookHandler->>TicketModel: update owner_holder_id
    WebhookHandler->>ClaimLinkModel: generate + notify
```

### 2. B2B Request Flow (Paid)

```
sequenceDiagram
    Organizer->>API: POST /api/organizers/b2b/events/{id}/requests
    API->>OrganizerService: create_b2b_request()
    Organizer->>API: POST .../confirm-payment
    API->>OrganizerService: confirm_b2b_payment()
    OrganizerService->>Razorpay: create_payment_link()
    OrganizerService-->>Organizer: payment_link_url
    Note over Organizer: Pays via Razorpay dashboard
    Razorpay->>Webhook: payment_link.paid
    WebhookHandler->>SuperAdminService: process_paid_b2b_allocation()
    SuperAdminService->>AllocationModel: create allocation
    WebhookHandler-->>Webhook: {status: ok}
```

### 3. B2B Transfer to Reseller

```
sequenceDiagram
    Organizer->>API: POST .../transfers/reseller
    API->>OrganizerService: create_b2b_transfer()
    OrganizerService->>TicketingRepository: lock_tickets()
    OrganizerService->>Razorpay: create_payment_link() [if paid]
    OrganizerService-->>Organizer: order + payment_link
    Note over Razorpay: Payment (if paid)
    Razorpay->>Webhook: payment_link.paid
    WebhookHandler->>OrderModel: update status=paid
    WebhookHandler->>AllocationModel: create (organizer→reseller)
    WebhookHandler->>TicketModel: update owner_holder_id
```

### 4. Ticket Claim (Customer receiving transfer)

```
sequenceDiagram
    Customer->>API: GET /api/open/claim/{token}
    API->>CoreService: validate_claim_link()
    CoreService->>TicketModel: find tickets by claim_link_id
    CoreService-->>Customer: ticket details + QR code
```

